<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-55-0426 </DOCNO><TEXT>Firstly this paper gives an historical survey on the origin and developmentof electromagnetic flowmeters. Then some theoretical points of theirworking are examined. The constitution of industrial devices is describedand some information on installation conditions and on metrological performancesare given. The last part deals with particular electromagnetic flowmeters,especially for liquid metals.</TEXT></DOC>